data.description: This charming property is in the heart of Cedar Key. Walk to everything. It features 1100 sq ft Conditioned area, and actual area of 1652 sq ft. Front & back porches to relax and enjoy the Cedar Key breeze. Double lot that can be split or you can add on or build another unit. TLC is all this home needs! It's a Single Family Old Historic Cedar Key home! Originally built in 1903, it shows a lot of history. Come add your finishing touches to this property and make it your own special retreat. Lots of privacy.
